              "desc": "華麗さと荘厳さを併せ持つ杯、千年前は美酒に満ちていた。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Archaic Petra/goblet_of_eonothem_icon.png",
