              "desc": "磯岩巨鳶の硬い羽根、玄石の羽先が露を凍らすことがたまにある。",
              "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/reliquary/Archaic Petra/plume_of_death_icon.png",
